      "amount": "10",
      "notes": "soaked 30 min"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat robata grill to medium‑high.",
    "Cut tofu into 1 cm cubes and pat dry.",
    "In a bowl mix soy sauce, mirin, sesame oil, minced garlic, salt and pepper.",
    "Thread alternating tomato, tofu, basil onto soaked skewers.",
    "Brush skewers with sauce mixture before grilling.",
    "Place skewers on robata grill and close lid.",
    "Grill 2–3 minutes on each side until tomatoes blister.",
    "Remove from grill, drizzle remaining sauce, and serve immediately."
  ],
